Awsome game!!!
The original Counter-Strike, is a game one cannot forget. Albeit having 3 successors, the gameplay of "the original" is incomparable. The title "Number 1 online action game" was truly deserved during its glory days. That said, the game is tactical, and the guns handle close to real-life counterparts. Either you plant a bomb, defuse a bomb, defend hostages or try rescuing them, there's also a few deathmatch maps, but the tactical/competitive gameplay is a lot better. If you find yourself struggling to get kills while revisiting one truly legendary game, try Condition Zero, as it's quite useful to understand the mechanics in the Counter-Strike franchise.
best tactical multiplayer shooter ever
