Best Old-School Fps Shooter~
Counter Strike is a game that will be in the gaming history books for centuries to come. It IS VALVe's turn in the competitive scene and this is their weapon. Counter-Strike. Stupendous game which has proven to many gamers that gameplay, strategy and quick thinking comes first and graphics second. Unique because of the ability to completely control the recoil of your weapon. Astounding as pretty much all the maps are beautifully designed, even now I appreciate the creativity, the player and modding bases allowing for some of the best content by the people, you to create. The gun mechanics are by far the best seen in any game I have ever played. The way the guns fire and flow syngerize and play so well, it's almost mad why they never copied this to CSS and CSGO. Planning rather than rushing is another reason. You never know what terrors come across. Counter Strike is no longer updated but however is still alive and played by most of Europe, where small teams and clans are still existing to this day. Veterans also still play this game (I don't play comp on this but I have met and played with players totalling 3000 hours on it, which is insane, inspiring and completely awesome!) the game itself, is in no way glitchy or bugged and is in fact, for a better word for it, near-perfection. VALVe will be remembered in the glory that is Counter Strike.
