Property Rating Explanation Graphics 5.5 The graphics of Counter-strike 1.6 are very dated compared to the next installments, CS: Source and CS:GO. Not really strong here. Gameplay 10 This is maybe the best, most addictive FPS multiplayer game ever created for PC. The gameplay is stellar. Multiplayer 9 Really addicting multiplayer, from public matches to gathers, mixed teams and clan clashes. Also, Valve's anti-cheat is present. Story N/A Multiplayer only. Sound-Music 7 The sound effects are very convincing, from gunshots to grenades and running. Optimization 9 Optimization is great, this game can run even on the more weak laptops without any problems. Cons N/A No achievements. Also many cheaters on public matches. No automatic ranked mode like CS:GO has. Overall 9 Best multiplayer FPS game ever created.
