Let's see... Where to start? I don't think there is a single person, who has ever played any FPS games and doesn't know CS 1.6. This is an epic game. An evergreen. A classic. This is where FPS gaming begins. Yea, it's a bit old, it's a bit buggy, the graphics are outdated, but that's how we love it. CS 1.6 is just perfect - well, on its own way. If you've never played it, buy it. 10/10
