Every Counter-Strike is a must buy. Not only are they all really fun, but it is really interesting to see the progression of them. 1.6 is the start of the series, and I thoroughly recommend looking up and downloading the original BETA maps from 1999 like Docks as they were originally part of the game (although most of them removed due to unfair map design [except Docks]). CS 1.6 is a fun game, but if you aren't interested in playing older games then I wouldn't bother, Source and Global Offensive are newer and more replay-friendly games.
