This game is massive time killer. It manages to be both simple and addictive, while having no customization, no unlocks, no achievements, nothing to distract you. This game will have tens of thousands of players from all over the world for all eternity. Those players are generally silent, but trolling and griefing is not at all unknown. This game is also very well known for cheaters. Several admins have bizarre rules that only make sense to them on their servers, so expect to be banned from a few. There are a few popular mods for this game, one being the Warcraft mod. You are generally required to read the notes on how to use these mods, but there are plenty of vanilla servers.
