Counter-Strike, originally a mod for Half-Life, is a game where you're put into the boots of counter-terrorists with a objective of stopping the other team, the terrorists (players can play as counter-terrorists or terrorists), from killing all of the pedestrians. True to the original Counter-Stike mod, it uses the GoldSrc engine. What I did dislike, however, is that the game is abandoned. If more players started playing, then this game could be so much better.
