Albeit being over a decade old, it's still an amazing game. I have played it both non steam and on steam, making total number of hours played well over 1500 Counter Strike does not come with built in game mode like deathmatch. Hence servers employ amxmodx [amxmodx.org] to create new game modes and modfy game experience of existing ones. Some of game mode I came across are: Deathmatch classic half life dm Capture The Flag A classic mode with each team having a flag and is required to bring opponents' flag to their base. Jailbreak A role play mod where prisoners must find a way to rebel and overthrow guards. Missile Mod Choose a missile from missile menu and kill your opponent. Beware, for your opponent has missiles too. PokeMod Pick up pokeballs lying around and choose active pokemon, you'll get its ability. For instance water pokemon give you heath regen while you are in water. Deathrun A path laid with terrorist controlled traps is awaiting to be crossed by a huge pack of Counter terrorists thristy for terrorist's blood. But if you fall off, you die. Hence deathrun. Hide n Seek Although the name says hide n seek, hiders don't hide. They simply run away and try to out trick seekers in a map skill and experience dependant. Hiders get an HE grenade, two flash grenades and a frost grenade while seekers have knives. Kreedz (KZ) KZ mod is a non violent mod where players find their way through curvings and tricks of map by use of strafe, bunny hop, etc. It is a 'sport' type game, where players compete for the best times amongst the game's several courses. Super Hero Mod You'll be given a list of heroes to choose from. You must choose two of them to get their powers. Trouble in Terrorist Town (TTT) This mod is about a group of "terrorists" who have traitors among them, out to kill everyone who's not a traitor. Cod There are various classes to select from, giving you different abilities including becoming near invisible when wielding a knife. Zombie Escape Zombies are infecting everyone around you and you must survive for given time period. Zombies with hp of over 2000(depending of server) are coming for your brains! If they infect you, you become one of them and carry out their mission: infect all humans. Surf Mod A fun mod with ramps all over map. You must surf these ramps and get kills by perching on a 'vantage' point to get kills(or to get killed) Nightcrawler Nightcrawlers are around you totally invisible. pay attention on your team mates, if one dies, you have an idea of where the nightcrawler was at that time. All in all, it is a very amazing game.
